{"tid":984503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跨黨派] 點名華為、中興通訊　美議員提案禁向違規華企售晶片","createTime":"2019-01-17T00:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T11:30:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc43dedb1bf9b1fd8260735d44cf503fa292e214","tid":984503,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:28:16.000Z","msg":"點名華為、中興通訊　議員提案禁向違規華企售晶片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190117/bkn-20190117071445563-0117_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117071445563-0117_00972_001.html&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=bb78f881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190117/bkn-20190117071445563-0117_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國共和民主兩黨一批國會議員周三（16日）提交法案，要求總統特朗普禁止向華為、中興通訊和其他違反美國制裁令或出口管制法的中國電訊公司，出售美國晶片或其他零部件。 <br />\n<br />\n據英媒報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">共和黨參議員柯頓、眾議員加拉格爾（Mike Gallagher）以及民主黨參議員范赫倫、眾議員加列戈（Ruben Gallego）聯合提出</span>上述法案，要求禁止對違規的中國電訊公司出口美國零部件。法案點名提到華為和中興通訊，兩間公司均涉嫌違反美國對伊朗的制裁令，其設備更被指可能用於監視美國人。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">柯頓的聲明中指摘：「華為實際上是中共用來收集情報的部門，其始創人和行政總裁是解放軍的工程師。如果像華為之類的中國電訊公司違反我們的制裁令或出口管制法，他們應受到不比『死刑』輕、這份出口權拒絕令會列明的懲罰。」 </span><br />\n<br />\n中興通訊曾因違反美國對伊朗的貿易禁運，去年4月被禁採購旗下手機等設備非常依賴的美國零部件。直至中興通訊同意繳交10億美元（約78億港元）罰款及4億美元（約31.2億港元）保證金，禁令才得以解除。"},{"pid":"d3887a9fe05a7e73553c1b4837d72ff536d9a133","tid":984503,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84306365b4160e36036f0b76a8c48ad9b294b694","tid":984503,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd7dcfa8b29eb9f3383e9c56b0001cf177b3c67","tid":984503,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:11:12.000Z","msg":"打啦，玩夠未姐"},{"pid":"5d82e723eefbb2adc7465296e30dae051355694a","tid":984503,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:15:15.000Z","msg":"［華為］ 日本不惜耗資拆除已安裝的華為通訊設備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/979966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/979966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4242a4e3cbbf40bf791a39936926db31a72f7aa7","tid":984503,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc623f94814f20f0fb0dcd15925eee49567355fb","tid":984503,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:27:19.000Z","msg":"全美自動波反支  好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a1bff3b80b8b3777296325581d363c055adae7","tid":984503,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"17b38673a8a1d51a2dd712340d031ba7d5e80e08","tid":984503,"uid":150347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"回憶小子,返來囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120612/720pix/12la9p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120612%2F720pix%2F12la9p3.jpg&h=8816a59f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa32c6e6e57482d628168c05b71eda22e5dd3595","tid":984503,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853c5320460d967503679ac2e2350df3f6554524","tid":984503,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:10:37.000Z","msg":"美國政治共識 反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0e4428c80d55ed8dc9eff0ea1f66dbf0bcb425","tid":98